STATE EX REL. FELTNER
v.
CUYAHOGA CTY. BD. OF REVISION 2018-1307 Supreme Court of Ohio. June 10, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENT

MISCELLANEOUS ORDER

In Mandamus and Prohibition. Sua sponte, relator's stipulation to extension of time to file reply brief stricken as untimely pursuant to S.Ct.Prac.R. 3.03(B)(2)(a). Relator may file a reply brief no later than June 25, 2019.
